%global rlibdir   /usr/local/lib/R/library

Name:             R-CRAN-%{packname}
Version:          3.1.1
Release:          1%{?dist}
Summary:          Non-Parametric Multiple Change-Point Analysis of MultivariateData

License:          GPL (>= 2)
URL:              https://cran.r-project.org/package=%{packname}
Source0:          %{url}&version=%{packver}#/%{packname}_%{packver}.tar.gz


BuildRequires:    R-devel >= 3.00
Requires:         R-core >= 3.00
BuildRequires:    R-CRAN-Rcpp 
Requires:         R-CRAN-Rcpp 

%description
Implements various procedures for finding multiple change-points. Two
methods make use of dynamic programming and pruning, with no
distributional assumptions other than the existence of certain absolute
moments in one method. Hierarchical and exact search methods are included.
All methods return the set of estimated change- points as well as other
summary information.

